    "Details": "Commissioned in 3042 by Imperator Marius O'Reilly, the Gladius Medium Hover Tank is a fast and simple combat vehicle. The Gladius is produced entirely on Alphard, with the exception of its single gun. The rugged design is heavily armored for a tank its size, mounting six tons of armor. The simple Internal combustion engine is cheap to produce and easy to repair and maintain.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>ICE: Air breathing Combustion Engine. This unit can not deploy in thin atmosphere.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 8/12 Hex: 240/360 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       150     20\n<b>Left</b>         120     20\n<b>Right</b>       120     20\n<b>Rear</b>         90     20\n\n<b>Total</b>      480     80</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Narrow/Low Profile</color>",
